cific africa middle east pakistan and europe is headquartered in singapore it is home to chevrons asiapacific headquarters for the manufacturing supply and trading marketing and lubricants operations chevron upstream has a presence in singapore through our shipping global gas and power generation businesses chevron asia pacific exploration and production also has a regional office in singapore other singapore operations include shipping global gas and power generation the caltex™ brand which serves customers in asia the middle east and africa is managed from singapore singapore is also chevron oronites regional headquarters for asiapacific and home to one of the largest fuel and lubricant additives manufacturing facility in asia who we hire where youll work how to apply compensation and benefits career development support who we hire chevron values integrity trust diversity and ingenuity as a company and in our employees in singapore chevron hires fulltime employees with the relevant education and experience we also look for individuals with the following qualities have a collaborative work style enjoy a diverse and teamworkoriented environment are solutionoriented and outcomedriven back to top where youll work depending on your role your journey at chevron could take you to one or more of these locations in singapore as well as to other locations around the globe jurong island — home to chevron oronites regional headquarters for asiapacific and singapore manufacturing plant raffles place — chevron downstream asia pacific headquarters is situated at chevron house it is also a regional hub for chevron upstream  gas jalan buroh — chevrons fuels terminal and lubricants blending plant click here to find out more about our business portfolio back to top how to apply singapore job openings if you are interested in combining your talents and ambition with those of our highperforming team please search and apply online only those candidates who are selected for an interview